# All Products Block

## Purpose

Renders all products from a selected collection in a client-side sortable CSS grid. Designed for small catalogs (~10 products). No pagination. Sorting is done entirely in JavaScript — no page reload.

## Usage

Must be placed inside a section that accepts `@theme` blocks (i.e. the section schema includes `{ "type": "@theme" }` in its `blocks` array).

```liquid
{% content_for 'block', type: 'all_products', id: 'all-products' %}
```

---

## Available Settings

### Content

| ID | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `collection` | collection | The collection whose products are displayed |

### Sorting

| ID | Type | Description | Default |
|---|---|---|---|
| `default_sort` | select | Which sort is active on load | `price-asc` |
| `show_sort_price_asc` | checkbox | Show "price low to high" option | true |
| `show_sort_price_desc` | checkbox | Show "price high to low" option | true |
| `show_sort_name_asc` | checkbox | Show "name A to Z" option | true |
| `show_sort_name_desc` | checkbox | Show "name Z to A" option | true |
| `sort_position` | select | Dropdown alignment — Left or Right | Left |
| `sort_font_size` | range (10–24px) | Dropdown font size | 14px |
| `sort_border_radius` | range (0–20px) | Dropdown corner radius | 0px |
| `sort_bg_color` | color | Dropdown background color | — |

The sort dropdown is hidden entirely when all four sort checkboxes are unchecked.

### Product card

| ID | Type | Description | Default |
|---|---|---|---|
| `card_info_layout` | select | Info area direction — Vertical (stacked) or Horizontal (side-by-side) | Vertical |
| `card_title_font_size` | range (10–32px) | Product title font size | 16px |
| `card_price_font_size` | range (10–24px) | Product price font size | 14px |

### Grid

| ID | Type | Description | Default |
|---|---|---|---|
| `columns` | range (1–8) | Number of desktop columns | 4 |
| `mobile_columns` | select (1 or 2) | Number of mobile columns | 2 |
| `columns_gap` | range (0–100px) | Horizontal gap between cards | 8px |
| `rows_gap` | range (0–100px) | Vertical gap between cards | 8px |

### Section layout

| ID | Type | Description | Default |
|---|---|---|---|
| `section_width` | select | Page-width or full-width | page-width |
| `color_scheme` | color_scheme | Color scheme | scheme-1 |

### Padding

| ID | Type | Description | Default |
|---|---|---|---|
| `padding-block-start` | range (0–100px) | Top padding | 48px |
| `padding-block-end` | range (0–100px) | Bottom padding | 48px |
